title: Jason Ravnsborg
deleted: On September 12, 2020, Ravnsborg hit and killed a pedestrian while driving home from a Republican political fundraiser. He had initially called 911 and reported that he had hit something that had damaged his car. An investigation of the collision was initiated by the Department of Public Safety.<ref>[https://www.cbsnews.com/news/jason-ravnsborg-south-dakota-attorney-general-revises-story-killing-man-with-car/ South Dakota attorney general now says he found body of man he hit with car and killed, CBS News, September 15, 2020, retrieved September 16, 2020]</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Here's what was said on the 911 call after Ravnsborg struck, killed a pedestrian |url=https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/crime/2020/10/13/jason-ravnsborg-fatal-crash-read-full-transcript-911-call/3640658001/ |website=Argus Leader |accessdate=14 October 2020 |date=13 October 2020}}</ref>
